	<!-- ==================== Ammo ========================== -->

	<ThingDef Class="CombatExtended.AmmoDef" ParentName="SpacerSmallAmmoBase">
		<defName>Ammo_ChargedLaser</defName>
		<label>Charged laser charge pack (US)</label>
		<description>An unstable (US) laser energy cell is a munition for high-tech weapons. It is a micro battery.\n\nWhen fired, the released energy of the munition is fed to the focusing component of the weapon, where a powerful high-temperature beam of light is formed for a fraction of a second. The power of an unstable cell is so great that it is difficult to create a sufficiently accurate laser, which is why it burns targets rather than pierces them like a stable laser cell.</description>
		<tradeTags>
			<li>CE_AutoEnableCrafting</li>
			<li>CE_AutoEnableTrade_Sellable</li>
		</tradeTags>
		<thingCategories>
			<li>AmmoLaser</li>
		</thingCategories>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Things/Ammo/LaserPack</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_StackCount</graphicClass>
		</graphicData>
		<statBases>
			<MarketValue>10</MarketValue>
			<Mass>0.01</Mass>
			<Bulk>0.02</Bulk>
		</statBases>
		<ammoClass>LaserUST</ammoClass>
	</ThingDef>  

	<ThingDef Class="CombatExtended.AmmoDef" ParentName="SpacerSmallAmmoBase">
		<defName>Ammo_ChargedLaser_Stable</defName>
		<label>Charged laser charge pack (S)</label>
		<description>Stable (S) laser energy cell - ammunition for high-tech weapons. It is a micro battery.\n\nWhen firing, the released energy of the ammunition is fed to the focusing component of the weapon, where a powerful high-temperature beam of light is formed for a split second. So pinpoint and concentrated that it literally perforates targets like bullets. Does not set targets on fire.</description>
		<tradeTags>
			<li>CE_AutoEnableCrafting</li>
			<li>CE_AutoEnableTrade_Sellable</li>
		</tradeTags>
		<thingCategories>
			<li>AmmoLaser</li>
		</thingCategories>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Things/Ammo/LaserPack</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_StackCount</graphicClass>
		</graphicData>
		<statBases>
			<MarketValue>11</MarketValue>
			<Mass>0.01</Mass>
			<Bulk>0.02</Bulk>
		</statBases>
		<ammoClass>LaserST</ammoClass>
		<thingSetMakerTags>
			<li>HSKCombatSuppliesAmmoAC</li>
		</thingSetMakerTags>
	</ThingDef>  

	<ThingDef Class="CombatExtended.AmmoDef" ParentName="SpacerSmallAmmoBase">
		<defName>Ammo_ChargedLaser_Electromagnetic</defName>
		<label>Charged laser charge pack (EM)</label>
		<description>Electromagnetic laser energy cell (EM) - ammunition for high-tech weapons. It is a microbattery.\n\nWhen firing, the released energy of the ammunition is fed to the focusing component of the weapon, where a powerful high-temperature beam of light is formed for a fraction of a second. This beam does not have high power or concentration, but transmits an electromagnetic pulse that allows damaging electrical devices and machines.</description>
		<tradeTags>
			<li>CE_AutoEnableCrafting</li>
